In the [[Māori mythology]] of the [[Ngāti Hau]] tribe, '''Hine-kau-ataata''' (Woman floating in shadow), is the daughter of [[Tiki (mythology)|Tiki]] (Man) and [[Mārikoriko]] (Twilight). When she is born, the first [[cloud]]s appear in the sky.

